Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berempat, majulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Murid-murid kelas satu\Ndari Asrama Cecile, yaitu Anya Forger,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Becky Blackbell,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Damian Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Murid kelas satu\Ndari Asrama Wald, Bill Watkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam insiden pembajakan bus tempo hari,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalian berperan besar\Nterhadap penyelesaiannya yang cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tetap tenang dan terkendali\Nselagi mendukung satu sama lain,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}serta berhasil melewati situasi kritis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tanpa ada korban.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atas keberanian, kebijaksanaan,\Ndan semangat kalian yang tangguh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bintang Stella dianugerahkan pada kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Bintang Stella pertamaku!\NAku sampai tak bisa berkata-kata!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah sewajarnya begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal, aku tak lakukan\Nhal yang pantas untuk ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tak benar, Damian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taktik "aku akan BAB di celana" itu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah kunci\Ndalam penyelesaian insiden ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dengar perusahaan surat kabar\Nmau mewawancarai kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga! Bagaimana kalau kita\Nmenjadi terkenal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kami tolak karena alasan keamanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pihak berwenang juga memperingatkan\Nagar tak menerima wawancara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, Dinas Keamanan Negara tak mau\Nanak-anak mencuri pujian dari mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Debutku sebagai penyanyi batal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harus Bapak bilang, sebuah keajaiban
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak ada anak yang terluka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}dalam situasi mengerikan itu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangkap para pelaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tim Penembak Runduk, kalian bebas tugas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bawa X1 sampai X3 ke Pos 13.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah aman.\NKau berjuang dengan sangat baik, Nak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan panggil aku "Nak"!\NAku pria dari keluarga Desmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sama sekali tak takut!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah boleh pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini palsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua sandera sudah terdata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Cabut perintah pembatasan media.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Telepon para orang tua dan wali,\Nserta minta mereka menjemput para murid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kami harus menemui mereka lagi\Ndi lain waktu untuk interogasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-Anak Asrama, pulanglah hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}- Ayah!\N- Becky! Syukurlah kau selamat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu ada di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah tak sudi membawa Ibu\Nke tempat berbahaya begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat khawatir di rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ayo pulang dan tenangkan dia.\N- Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau apa kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa. Ini tak menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang selalu mengejekmu, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku mau bilang aku minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga keren, Putra Kedua!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat mengajukan diri untuk mengambil\Nbom Anya, kau seperti pahlawan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu... Itu bukan hal istimewa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu... Menolong teman itu wajar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anya sudah menjadi teman baikmu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Ibu. Sepertinya Anya\Nyang akan memenangkan pertempuran ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bicara apa? Lagi pula,\Naku tak pernah bilang teman "baik".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Besok, aku akan ke rumahmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesama teman biasanya saling berkunjung\Nke rumah, memperkenalkan orang tua,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}serta bicara soal perdamaian\Ndan semacamnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku harus mengundangmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, mana ada orang yang mengenalkan\Norang tuanya dan membahas perdamaian?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan ini? Ternyata, kau memang\Ncuma mengincar nama Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hampir saja tertipu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bukan temanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak lihat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan ada yang menjemputku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski menjilatku,\Nkau tak akan bisa mendekati orang tuaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan! Orang tuamu\Njuga tak ada di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-anak yang tak dijemput\Nakan diantar oleh polisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku bisa naik mobil polisi? Seru!\N- Anya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Anya!\N- Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencari ke mana-mana\Ndan baru dengar beritanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berlari ke sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada luka? Apa kau terluka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau ditikam, ditembak, ditindih,\Ndicabik-cabik, atau semacamnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada lagi yang harus ditakuti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku tak bisa\Nmenyelamatkanmu lebih cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan tungsten... Syukurlah\Ndia bersikap seperti anak seusianya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Payah sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang mengira ini selesai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebelum Unit Penyerbu masuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya tak ada gunanya\Nkau bergegas ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ayah juga ada di sini!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak tahu apa yang terjadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kalau sudah selesai,\Naku akan kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berada di tengah\NDinas Keamanan Negara seperti ini
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak baik untuk perutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak perlu melakukan\Nreuni yang penuh air mata dengan putrimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dokter Loid Forger seharusnya\Nsedang dalam perjalanan bisnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil tiba secepat ini\Nsetelah dengar beritanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti terlihat mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku sudah pulang, akan kubuatkan\Nmasakan favorit dia atau semacamnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Steik Hamburg!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kau Damian, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam perjalanan ke sini,\Naku melihat mobil Melinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berlari melewatinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku yakin dia akan segera tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Rekan Rencana Pertemanan Ibu! Rivalku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Damian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Damian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu datang untuk aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang apa? Tentu saja Ibu datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena baru dengar beritanya,\NIbu tak bisa datang lebih cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Damian. Damian, Damian-ku tersayang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jika sesuatu terjadi padamu,\Naku harus bagaimana? Damian...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Damian-ku yang manis...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, Ibu bersyukur kau selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia sama seperti Paman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sama sekali tak takut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya kesal\Nkarena tak bisa mengunjungi museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu memaksakan diri begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Jangan beri tahu Ayah bahwa aku menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku tak mau Ayah khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Seharusnya aku tak ke sini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa Ibu katakan itu padanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya Ibu yang memastikan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tak memberi tahu pria itu\Nbahwa Ibu datang ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Andai saja dia mati dalam insiden ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Syukurlah dia tak apa-apa.\NAku tak peduli. Merepotkan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kenapa dia tak pulang sendiri saja?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia pura-pura kuat. Imutnya.\NMungkin aku harus memasak untuknya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Andai saja dia tak ada. Dia hartaku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia kutukanku. Aku menyayangimu, Damian.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berjanjilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Cahaya Bintang, Cahaya Bintang{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Cahaya Bintang Anya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paprikanya jangan disisakan, Anya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Cahaya Bintang Anya.\NJadi, aku tak perlu memakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Logika macam apa itu? Makanlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang bagus kau dapat Bintang Stella,\Ntapi melawan para pembajak dengan gegabah
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukan hal yang patut dipuji, tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Kau tak boleh melakukan\Nhal berbahaya seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Profesorku juga bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kudengar kau meminta makanan\Ndari para pembajak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anya saat itu lapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti karena sarapan yang kubuat\Ntak cukup bergizi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kegiatan belajar\Ndimulai lagi hari ini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kuantar kau ke sekolah.\NHabiskan makananmu, lalu ganti baju.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia tampaknya baik-baik saja,\Ntapi yang dia alami pasti traumatis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku harus memperlakukan dia\Ndengan hati-hati.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mobil Ayah itu mobil yang sudah usang{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Lebih kecil dari bus dan rasanya sempit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Oh, sangat sempit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mobil Becky sangat luas dan berkilau{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mungkin dia tak mengalami trauma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempo hari, Ibu dan aku naik mobil polisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lajunya cepat dan sangat menyenangkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?\NPolisi yang mengantar kalian pulang, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku tak bisa menjemputmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ayah ada di sana.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau keluarga mereka datang menjemput,\Napa artinya mereka dekat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa bisa dibilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di situasi seperti itu, aku yakin sebagian\Nbesar akan jemput anak mereka. Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski menjilatku,\Nkau tak akan bisa mendekati orang tuaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Damian!\N- Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Damian. Merepotkan. Dia kutukanku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berjanjilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Keluarga Putra Kedua sangat aneh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa dia memang kesal\Nkarena aku tak menjemputnya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Benar juga. Seperti kebanyakan anak\Ndi panti asuhan, dia pasti habiskan hidup{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}menunggu seseorang menjemputnya\Ntanpa hasil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu menyebabkan luka batin yang dalam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku harus menyembuhkannya, atau itu\Nbisa memengaruhi misiku. Bagaimana ini?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anya sedang mau makan keik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita beli sepulang sekolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Keik terlezat yang pernah ada!\N- Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah merasa lebih baik?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kadang masih mengalami kilas balik,\Ndan itu membuatku gemetar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau mau, aku bisa memperkenalkanmu\Npada psikiater tepercaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alih-alih diriku,\Naku lebih mencemaskan para murid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, tapi agar bisa merawat mereka,\Nkita juga harus menjaga kesehatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku teringat,\Nkudengar rapat orang tua dan wali
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang diadakan kemarin cukup sulit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tak ada lagi yang berani berbicara
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}setelah Dinas Keamanan Negara\Ntiba-tiba masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi wajar saja para orang tua\Nmerasa khawatir dan marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai tenaga pengajar,\Nkita harus lakukan apa pun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk mendukung para murid\Ndan orang tua mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga harimu menyenangkan, Tuan Muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selamat pagi, Damian!\N- Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya aneh diantar ke sekolah\Ndengan mobil, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau menikmati waktumu di rumah\Nsetelah sekian lama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Jeeves. Ibu di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah kembali ke vilanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku diminta merahasiakannya.\NJadi, aku hanya bicara sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi semua hidangan yang sedang kau makan\Ndimasak oleh ibumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku turut senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bayangkan, kita kembali\Nke kehidupan asrama yang ketat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Damian!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga! Aku bicara dengan dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka dari Kelas 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, kau dianggap\Npenyelamat Kelas 3 dan 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?\N- Becky! Selamat pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Becky, rencana SOS-mu luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Anya si Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hebat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau keren sekali saat menghadapi\Npara pembajak itu, Anya si Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panggil aku Cahaya Bintang Ganda Anya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cahaya Bintang Ganda Anya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hei, Forger. Selamat pagi.\N- Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Anya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku sudah bicara buruk tentangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak takut pada bom itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kau meyakinkan penjahat itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selamat pagi, Forger.\N- Mau ke kelas
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- bersama-sama?\N- Ayo makan siang bersama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sepertinya ini zamannya Anya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Gawat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Aku sekarang sangat populer,\Nbisa-bisa dapat 100 teman!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dengan teman sebanyak itu,\Naku mungkin bisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}menaklukkan dunia!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sok sekali. Dasar bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Astaga. Kau cemburu?\N- Yang benar saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika semua orang\Nmulai menyadari pesona Anya,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin akan ada yang datang\Ndan merebut hatinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku tak merinding!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku tak punya perasaan apa pun\Nterhadap gadis payah itu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Meyakinkan" apanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia cuma rakyat jelata yang lapar\Ndan berteriak minta makan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah apa yang membuat\Npara pembajak menyerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat! Kau rakyat jelata,\Ntapi bisa masuk Akademi Eden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti susah sekali, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantas saja dia bisa melawan\Npara pembajak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika menjadi rakyat jelata,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akankah aku menjadi kuat sepertimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ajarkan kami rahasia\Nmenjadi rakyat jelata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Apa yang dimakan rakyat jelata?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nikmatilah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gumpalan hitam hangus\Ndan makanan lancip yang terasa asin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rakyat jelata memakan makanan seperti itu\Nuntuk memperkuat perut?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantas saja mereka menjadi sangat kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka sangat miskin, sampai-sampai\Norang tua mereka yang memasak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Itu payah sekali. Benar, Damian?\N- Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang salah dari itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Masakan Ibu rasanya lezat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Damian, akhir-akhir ini\Nkau bersikap lembut terhadapnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Tidak! Aku sangat kasar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan beri tahu Ayah bahwa aku menangis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Putra Kedua yang manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Tapi Ibu benci anak lemah yang cengeng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang bilang kita bisa menjadi kuat\Nkalau berperilaku seperti Anya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hidup rakyat jelata!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau menjadi anak yang kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku datang ke rumah Anya\Nuntuk belajar cara menjadi rakyat jelata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Bersama orang tuaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kutitipkan Putra Kedua pada kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Kenapa tak terpikir olehku?\NUntuk Rencana B, Strategi Pertemanan,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Anya hanya memikirkan cara\Nuntuk mengunjungi rumah Putra Kedua.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi aku bisa saja\Nmengundang Putra Kedua ke rumahku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Benar. Dengan kata lain,\Nini versi terbalik Rencana B.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Akan kusebut...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}...B Rencana.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak takut memakan sesuatu seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku makan tiap hari,\Nmeski tahu bisa saja mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Serius?\N{\i1}- Aku harus tunjukkan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}betapa kuatnya keluargaku\Npada Putra Kedua.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan latihan siang dan malam,\Nkalian bisa menjadi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}anak kuat yang tak cengeng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar pembohong.\NWaktu itu, kau menangis keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa lagi? Apa yang kau lakukan\Npada hari biasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terus-terusan dipaksa belajar
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}oleh Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah mengerjakan PR?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cukup normal, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, saat kami pergi berbelanja\Ndi supermarket,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka menyuruh Anya\Nmembawa barang-barang berat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anya yang pegang camilannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan dimakan sebelum dibayar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, itu caramu membesarkan otot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berbelanja sendiri? Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, sikat gigi kami\Nberatnya sekitar 100 kilogram.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suhu air mandi kami\Nsekitar 100 derajat Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, Anya melawan\Nseekor monster putih tiap hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Gawat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Anya mulai melebih-lebihkan lagi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia bisa dianggap pembohong lagi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa rahasia di balik kekuatan Anya\Nada pada latihan dari ibunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibunya sangat kuat, tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga melatihku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia berusaha merenggut popularitas Anya\Ndan mengalihkannya pada Ibu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Becky, apa kau mata-mata\Nyang berusaha mengganggu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pertarungan Rencana Pertemanan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kami datang ke rumahmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa dia juga akan melatih kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Tidak. Kalian tak akan menjadi lebih kuat\Nmeski datang ke rumahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Leher Ibu patah.\NJadi, Ibu sedang beristirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?\N- Lehernya patah, tapi masih hidup?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ibunya rakyat jelata hebat!\N- Semoga cepat sembuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anya yang akan mengajari kalian!\NAyo memukul seperti ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sangat informatif, Forger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh sekali! Semuanya, hentikan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berteman dengan dia\Nhanya akan mengotori nama keluarga kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putra Kedua juga mau menyabotase\Npopularitas Anya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak salah soal itu.\NDia memang cemburu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak bermaksud begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku membencimu, Putra Kedua. Berengsek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:20:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kau bilang apa? Aku lebih membencimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar gadis berkaki pendek,\Nbodoh, tak berguna,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jelek, serakah, juga seperti hiena!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibumu seekor gorila!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahmu penipu dan tukang suap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Kemampuanmu menyerang\Ndengan kata-kata sudah meningkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kaki Anya tak pendek.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Damian membuat Forger menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu berarti Damian lebih kuat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Keluarga Desmond memang hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Anya yang paling kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau menaklukkan dunia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang apa, Anya? Tenanglah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berhasil, Damian! Kau menang telak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan membawa camilan\Nsebagai permintaan maaf kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, jangan menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa Damian...\N- Meminta maaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belnya berbunyi! Ayo ke kelas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia meminta maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam! Sudah kubilang, bukan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahu apa kata orang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang bisa meminta maaf\Nadalah orang yang benar-benar kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku menang!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Begitu rupanya!\N- Damian memang luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anya tak kalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?\N- Anya lebih kuat daripada kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa? Kau baru saja menangis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yang menangis saat dijemput.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan katakan itu keras-keras! Sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sendiri yang menangis keras\Nsampai ingusmu berlepotan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, Anya imut.\NJadi, aku tak punya ingus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang dirimu imut? Kau bodoh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang bilang orang lain bodoh\Nbiasanya lebih bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam! Bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putra Kedua cuma tahu kata "bodoh".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau membuatku kesal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:21:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kemudian, mereka berdua\Nterlambat masuk kelas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Terjemahan subtitle oleh Diajeng Tyagita A
